{"tid":1027663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗突取消德甲直播　因為女球證著短褲","createTime":"2019-02-19T03:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T03:42:40.000Z","uid":23707,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c4058caeae604a4ec08fe8becf2c7803063b4591","tid":1027663,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"德國傳媒報道，上周五德甲拜仁慕尼黑作客贏奧格斯堡3比2，當日伊朗電視台突然取消直播，事後調查所得，原因係為比賽執法係一位女球證，而且該女球證著短褲亮相。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗電視台原定直播比賽，但臨時取消都係被迫，根據伊斯蘭教規定，當地電視台唔可以播放女性自己穿着畫面，例如不能穿運動短褲出現。雖然好多伊朗球迷都不滿今次突然禁播，但既然係宗教信仰，佢哋亦唯有遵守。<br />\n<br />\n至於為今場執法嘅女球證，就係39歲嘅比比安娜‧施泰因豪斯，估唔到佢嘅出現，搞到伊朗球迷冇得睇波。"},{"pid":"c575b8b0af70e40c85391d97f271b8b30707befd","tid":1027663,"uid":88763,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/InsistentNegligibleKinglet-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FInsistentNegligibleKinglet-size_restricted.gif&h=8f243fc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbd80790013c08c241a41ae351ec88e9a6f04f6e","tid":1027663,"uid":38472,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"蛔真係第一大有毒宗教。"},{"pid":"edc98d4e8913a398dec11743dc0d4112212e60c1","tid":1027663,"uid":34666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c575b8b0af70e40c85391d97f271b8b30707befd","tid":1027663,"uid":88763,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/InsistentNegligibleKinglet-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FInsistentNegligibleKinglet-size_restricted.gif&h=8f243fc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"睇樣點睇得出係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e3615c6c183fc0b0be491b645a7368a6115650","tid":1027663,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"